** [http://openjdk.java.net/ Java 1.7 OpenJDK]
** [http://www.opendaylight.org/software OpenDaylight release distributions]
** [http://mininet.org/ mininet 2.1.0]
** [http://openvswitch.org/ Open vSwitch 2.0.0]
** [http://www.wireshark.org/ Wireshark]
** [http://www.openstack.org/ OpenStack]
* VM configuration:
** Fedora 20, 20GB HDD, ova file size=1.5GB (or) Fedora 19, 20GB HDD, ova file size=3GB

